Package: tidybreed
Type: Package
Title: Tidy Breeding Program Simulation
Version: 0.11.1
Authors@R:
    person("Austin", "Putz", , "putz.austin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6459-7123"))
Description: A next-generation R package for breeding program simulation that
    uses tidyverse-style design and pipe operators. Provides flexible,
    memory-efficient tools for simulating animal and plant breeding programs
    with support for complex mating designs, trait architectures, and selection
    strategies.
